### We welcome the new GIRFT report calling for vital improvements in diabetes
### Melin Primary school in Neath wins good diabetes care award
Melin Primary School was awarded the Diabetes UK ‘Good Diabetes Care in School
Award 2020’. It was chosen because of the support it provides to pupils with
the condition, the help it offers to manage their diabetes safely, and the
care it takes to include them in all school activities.
